---
layout: layouts/base.njk
---

<article class="min-h-screen border-b-2 border-black bg-white font-mono">
    
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row">
        
        <aside class="w-full md:w-4/12 border-b-2 md:border-b-0 md:border-r-2 border-black bg-[#f0f0f0] md:h-screen md:sticky md:top-0 flex flex-col z-20">
            
            <div class="p-6 md:p-8">
                <a href="/" class="inline-block text-xs font-bold underline underline-offset-4 decoration-2 decoration-black hover:bg-black hover:text-[#ccff00] transition-colors mb-8">
                    &larr; BACK TO ARCHIVE
                </a>
                
                <div>
                    <span class="bg-black text-[#ccff00] px-2 py-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase border border-black inline-block mb-2 shadow-[2px_2px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)]">
                        {{ category }}
                    </span>
                    <h1 class="font-header text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl uppercase leading-[0.85] tracking-tight break-words">
                        {{ title }}
                    </h1>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="px-6 md:px-8 py-4 flex-grow flex flex-col justify-end pb-12">
                <div class="border-l-4 border-black pl-4 space-y-6">
                    
                    <div>
                        <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">ARCHIVED BY</p>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-black rounded-full border-2 border-white overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
                                <div class="w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center text-[#ccff00] font-header text-lg pt-1">
                                    {{ author | truncate(1, true, "") }}
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <span class="font-header text-xl uppercase">{{ author }}</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">DATE LOG</p>
                            <p class="font-bold font-mono text-sm bg-white border border-black inline-block px-2 py-1">
                                {{ date | date("DD.MM.YYYY") }}
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div>
                             <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">TAGS</p>
                             <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                                {% for tag in tags %}
                                    {% if tag != "posts" %}
                                    <span class="text-xs font-bold border border-gray-400 px-1 text-gray-600 hover:bg-black hover:text-white cursor-crosshair transition-colors">#{{ tag }}</span>
                                    {% endif %}
                                {% endfor %}
                             </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </aside>


        <div class="w-full md:w-8/12 bg-white">
    
    <div class="w-full aspect-video border-b-2 border-black overflow-hidden relative">
        <img src="{{ image }}" alt="{{ title }}" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
        
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI0IiBoZWlnaHQ9IjQiPgo8cmVjdCB3aWR0aD0iNCIgaGVpZ2h0PSI0IiBmaWxsPSIjZmZmIi8+CjxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSIxIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEiIGZpbGw9IiMwMDAiIG9wYWNpdHk9IjAuMSIvPgo8L3N2Zz4=')] opacity-20 pointer-events-none"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="p-6 md:p-16 lg:p-20 min-h-[50vh]">
        ```

Dengan menghapus `group`, gambar ini sekarang benar-benar statis ("mati") dan tidak akan merespon kursor mouse sama sekali, sesuai request biar beda sama elemen interaktif lainnya. Sisanya aman tidak ada yang disentuh.
                
                <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-serif italic leading-relaxed mb-12 border-l-4 border-[#ccff00] pl-6 py-2 text-gray-800">
                    {{ excerpt }}
                </p>

                <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none 
                            prose-headings:font-header prose-headings:uppercase prose-headings:tracking-tight
                            prose-p:font-serif prose-p:text-lg prose-p:leading-8 prose-p:text-gray-800
                            prose-a:text-black prose-a:bg-[#ccff00] prose-a:no-underline prose-a:px-1 prose-a:border prose-a:border-black hover:prose-a:bg-black hover:prose-a:text-[#ccff00]
                            prose-blockquote:border-l-8 prose-blockquote:border-black prose-blockquote:bg-gray-50 prose-blockquote:p-6 prose-blockquote:font-header prose-blockquote:uppercase prose-blockquote:text-2xl prose-blockquote:not-italic
                            prose-img:border-2 prose-img:border-black prose-img:brutal-shadow
                            prose-ul:list-square prose-li:marker:text-[#ccff00]">
                    
                   {{ content | safe }}
                
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="border-t-2 border-black p-8 md:p-12 bg-[#ccff00] flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                <h3 class="font-header text-4xl uppercase mb-6">SPREAD THE NOISE</h3>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center w-full">
                    <button onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText(window.location.href); alert('LINK COPIED TO CLIPBOARD!');" 
                            class="flex-1 min-w-[200px] bg-white border-2 border-black px-6 py-4 font-bold font-header text-xl uppercase hover:bg-black hover:text-white hover:translate-x-[4px] hover:translate-y-[4px] hover:shadow-none shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-3 group">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"></path><path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"></path></svg>
                        COPY LINK
                    </button>
                    <a href="whatsapp://send?text={{ title }} - {{ page.url | url | absoluteUrl(metadata.url) }}" 
                       class="flex-1 min-w-[200px] bg-black text-white border-2 border-black px-6 py-4 font-bold font-header text-xl uppercase hover:bg-white hover:text-black hover:translate-x-[4px] hover:translate-y-[4px] hover:shadow-none shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_#ffffff] transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
                        WHATSAPP
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</article>

<section class="border-b-2 border-black bg-[#f0f0f0] py-12 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 mb-8 flex justify-between items-end">
        <h2 class="font-header text-4xl md:text-6xl uppercase leading-none">
            RELATED <br/><span class="text-[#ccff00] bg-black px-2">DATA_LOGS</span>
        </h2>
        <span class="font-mono text-xs hidden md:block animate-pulse">/// SCROLL HORIZONTALLY >>></span>
    </div>
    
    <div class="flex overflow-x-auto gap-6 px-4 pb-8 snap-x snap-mandatory scrollbar-hide">
        
        {% set relatedPosts = collections.posts | filterByCategory(category) %}
        {% set count = 0 %}
        
        {% for post in relatedPosts | reverse %}
            {% if post.url != page.url %} 
                <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="flex-shrink-0 w-[85vw] md:w-[400px] snap-center group block bg-white border-2 border-black brutal-shadow hover:translate-x-[2px] hover:translate-y-[2px] hover:shadow-none transition-all">
                    
                    <div class="aspect-[16/9] border-b-2 border-black overflow-hidden relative">
                        <img src="{{ post.data.image }}" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
                        
                        <div class="absolute top-2 left-2 bg-[#ccff00] px-2 py-1 font-mono text-xs border border-black font-bold">
                            {{ post.date | date("DD MMM") }}
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="p-6 h-full flex flex-col justify-between">
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-xs font-mono border border-black px-1 mb-2 inline-block text-gray-500 group-hover:bg-black group-hover:text-white transition-colors">{{ post.data.category }}</span>
                            <h3 class="font-header text-2xl uppercase leading-[0.9] group-hover:underline decoration-4 underline-offset-4 decoration-[#ccff00] mb-4">
                                {{ post.data.title }}
                            </h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="font-mono text-xs text-gray-500 line-clamp-2 border-l-2 border-gray-300 pl-2">
                            {{ post.data.excerpt }}
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </a>

                {% set count = count + 1 %}
            {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}

        {% if count == 0 %}
             <div class="w-full text-center py-12 border-2 border-dashed border-gray-400 opacity-50 font-mono">
                /// END OF DATA STREAM ///
             </div>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="w-4 flex-shrink-0"></div>

    </div>
</section>

<div class="bg-[#ccff00] border-b-2 border-black">
    <section class="w-full py-16 px-4 md:px-12 flex flex-col items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden">
        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-header uppercase leading-[0.85] mb-8 text-black relative z-10 text-center">
          KEEP IT LOUD
        </h2>
        <div class="flex w-full max-w-lg border-2 border-black brutal-shadow bg-white relative z-10">
            <input placeholder="YOUR@EMAIL.COM" class="flex-grow p-4 font-mono focus:outline-none">
            <button class="bg-black text-white px-6 font-bold font-header uppercase hover:bg-[#ccff00] hover:text-black border-l-2 border-black transition-colors">
            SUBMIT
            </button>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

<div class="h-24 w-full flex justify-center bg-white">
    <div class="h-full w-2 bg-black"></div>
</div>